      "originalText": "authController.js      — register, login, OTP, reset password\njobController.js       — create/read/update/delete jobs\napplicationController  — createApplication() stores atsScore,\n                         atsGrade, atsCategory, atsBreakdown,\n                         atsFeedback from req.body\nclientController.js    — client profile & job management\nmessageController.js   — send/fetch direct messages\ncrewController.js      — crew/team features",
