      "originalText": "scorer.py  — NLP + Rule-Based Scoring\n  clean_resume_text()   remove URLs/phones/symbols\n  lemmatize_text()      NLTK WordNetLemmatizer\n  score_sections()      max 25  — Education/Skills/etc\n  score_keywords()      max 25  — industry power words\n  score_quantified_impact() max 20 — numbers/metrics\n  score_action_verbs()  max 15  — managed/built/led\n  score_readability()   max 10  — Flesch Reading Ease\n  score_contact_info()  max  5  — email + phone",
