      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ML Pipeline  model/*.pkl\n  tfidf_vectorizer.pkl  → text → TF-IDF sparse matrix\n  ats_scaler.pkl        → StandardScaler on numeric feats\n  hstack([tfidf_vec, scaled_feats])  → combined input\n  best_ats_model.pkl    → predict(X) → job category\n  label_encoder.pkl     → decode number → category name\n  predict_proba()       → confidence %",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.1071428571428572
